{"tid":1594892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拗撚夠跳閘未呀？","createTime":"2019-09-25T19:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T20:05:46.000Z","uid":230239,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b194094002ab1b37f732d1fb90fc8e19b562751e","tid":1594892,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:17:45.000Z","msg":"唔跳嘅話跳閘送頭<br />\n跳嘅話唔跳懦弱<br />\n然後瘋狂開po拗<br />\n呢個咪係分化囉<br />\n又話兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n之後又變返互屌<br />\n解決唔到跳閘問題之餘仲洗埋版<br />\n三毛嘅目的就達成喇<br />\n<br />\n唔跳嘅手足唔好再開po叫停<br />\n有啲人唔睇連登<br />\n你冇可能淨係出po就解決到問題<br />\n而且而家根本冇共識<br />\n月頭拗到月尾都係咁<br />\n你出po勸止唔會有用<br />\n<br />\n至於跳嘅手足<br />\n我相信而家仲堅持跳嘅多數都識得保護自己<br />\n呢樣嘢我唔太擔心<br />\n不過都對唔跳嘅人寬容啲<br />\n唔好屌人/逼佢哋跟自己嗰套<br />\n大把不合作方法可以對抗黨鐵<br />\n都係嗰八個字啦<br />\n<br />\n非必要嘅話唔好再推跳閘爭論po<br />\n多謝各位手足"},{"pid":"15a234d227406cfd547dcba15492eefcb562dbdc","tid":1594892,"uid":171087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:21:00.000Z","msg":"跳就跳 唔跳就唔跳<br />\n就好似勇武和理要共存一樣<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力，勿忘初心"},{"pid":"670494ac9ff1a7179725a726584517f917163f99","tid":1594892,"uid":230239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"15a234d227406cfd547dcba15492eefcb562dbdc","tid":1594892,"uid":171087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:21:00.000Z","msg":"跳就跳 唔跳就唔跳<br />\n就好似勇武和理要共存一樣<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力，勿忘初心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:22:05.000Z","msg":"不分化 不指責"},{"pid":"82e5f1e5e3731e406dcfb8660ad02fdd75f7014d","tid":1594892,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:24:42.000Z","msg":"凌晨三毛開工負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf9915fd5a67d87f082a923f95989058c4d6463","tid":1594892,"uid":287735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:25:05.000Z","msg":"成日鬧人分化撚嘅先係真係嘅分化撚<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1594895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1594895</a><br />\n<br />\n不分化、不指責!<br />\n主推行動Post<br />\np牌推唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ca9d5e20d4aa09c25e0d08b94aae65cd3136aa","tid":1594892,"uid":230239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:33:15.000Z","msg":"拗跳閘嘅就光速上熱門推到停唔到<br />\n呢個po就冇聲氣<br />\n連登被滲透嘅情況好得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5749585b403a22703c0b0f7296ae79bb7626ca","tid":1594892,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:34:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11dba5e18d3fc91502611acd42c30bcae5f4da52","tid":1594892,"uid":168730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:34:48.000Z","msg":"跳得既都有咁上下身手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9519e7d9538d031b867b4acf435c4743bff9b27f","tid":1594892,"uid":282798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:39:17.000Z","msg":"何必太執着<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識執生就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦唔需要夾硬嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53cd4b5b4d21914002fb58d098241e87769ce0c6","tid":1594892,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:05:46.000Z","msg":"想跳咪跳，唔想跳咪唔跳<br />\n3個月前叫各有各做兄弟爬山<br />\n依家就迫人埋堆爬<br />\n俾人捉到跳閘咪去幫佢解圍中lo<br />\n留番時間諗新招對抗黨鐵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}